<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="86" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="19" pageNumber="86">
<pageBreakToken pageId="19" pageNumber="86" start="start">Culture</pageBreakToken>
characters.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="19" pageNumber="86">On PDA, cultures are initially white, turning purple after 2 weeks on PDA. The colonies are flat with irregular edge; texture uniform, producing concentric circles within 1 month at 25 °C in the dark.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
