</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="86" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="19" pageNumber="86">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="19" pageNumber="86">
<taxonomicName class="Sordariomycetes" genus="Dendrostoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Dendrostoma shaanxiense" order="Diaporthales" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="shaanxiense">Dendrostoma shaanxiense</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. castaneae" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" rank="species" species="castaneae">D. castaneae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. castaneicola" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" rank="species" species="castaneicola">D. castaneicola</taxonomicName>
are phylogenetically closely related species occurring on the same host, 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Castanea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Castanea mollissima" order="Fagales" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="mollissima">Castanea mollissima</taxonomicName>
(Fig. 2). However, 
<taxonomicName class="Sordariomycetes" genus="Dendrostoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Dendrostoma shaanxiense" order="Diaporthales" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="shaanxiense">Dendrostoma shaanxiense</taxonomicName>
has conidia with a smaller l/w ratio than 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. castaneae" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" rank="species" species="castaneae">D. castaneae</taxonomicName>
(3.3-4.2 in 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. shaanxiense" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" rank="species" species="shaanxiense">D. shaanxiense</taxonomicName>
vs. 4.2-5.2 in 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. castaneae" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" rank="species" species="castaneae">D. castaneae</taxonomicName>
) and has narrower conidia than 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. castaneicola" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" rank="species" species="castaneicola">D. castaneicola</taxonomicName>
(2.5-3.1 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
diam. in 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. shaanxiense" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" rank="species" species="shaanxiense">D. shaanxiense</taxonomicName>
vs. 3.2-3.8 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
diam. in 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. castaneicola" pageId="19" pageNumber="86" rank="species" species="castaneicola">D. castaneicola</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
